msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "You piece of shit... Whaddya think\r\nyou were doing to our Yuka-chan!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "You might be the Kabedon Prince, but\r\nthat don't give ya the right to mess with her!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Kabedon...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "I told you, it was just for the show!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Yuka-san and I have nothing\r\ngoing on in real life, I swear!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Shut your face! I don't care if it's real or not.\r\nYou... You kabedon'd our sweet Yuka-chan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "I ain't gonna forgive you, pretty boy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Hey. That's enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "What, you want a taste of this, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure what's going on here, but three\r\nof you versus one of him? Doesn't seem fair."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Nobody asked for your opinion, gramps!\r\nWe're gonna make you pay for messing with us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "What... What the hell <font_kind=yakuza_italic>are</font_kind> you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Y-You totally saved my skin...\r\nThank you so much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Um, I'm Junta Takayama. I don't mean to pry,\r\nbut could you tell me your name?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san it is, then. Um, if it's all right with\r\nyou, could I repay you for this somehow?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "I was just helping a civilian in need.\r\nNo need to thank me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Come on, let me do <font_kind=yakuza_italic>something</font_kind>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "That's it! You know the bar Bantam, right?\r\nI spend most of my time drinking over there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "If you're ever free, I'd like to at least\r\nbuy you a round of drinks to say thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "All right, then.\r\nI'll stop by if I'm feeling thirsty."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Yes, please do. \r\nWell, I'll be going now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!\r\nI'm so glad you came!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "I have to say, I really had my back to the wall\r\nwhen you showed up. Thank you so much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "The truth is, I'm an actor. I can't exactly\r\nraise a fist to my potential audience."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Understandable. Life is pretty rough\r\nin the entertainment industry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "But I have to wonder, what were\r\nthose guys so upset with you about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Well... They're fans of a famous\r\nidol who goes by the name Yuka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "In a recent episode, I kabedon'd Yuka-chan\r\nreal good. I guess they were upset about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Kabedon...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Yes. Drama aficionados have actually\r\nstarted calling me the Kabedon Prince."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Huh...\r\nSorry, but I don't follow TV too closely."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "So... What exactly is kabedon?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Wait, you don't know?\r\nIt's really taken off lately."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "I'm pretty sure I've eaten a kabedon before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Oh, you're probably talking about katsudon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "It's the mythological guy with the trident, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Are you sure you don't mean Poseidon?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Is that where you hit the wall\r\nto make your neighbors quiet down?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "You're not technically wrong... but the kind\r\nI'm talking about is not quite the same."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Kabedon is, well...\r\nYou know, it might be quicker to just show you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, please stand\r\nin front of the wall over there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Yes, that's perfect."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Now then, here I come."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Hold on a second!\r\nWhat are you doing!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Well?\r\nThis is the magic of kabedon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "From here, a girl's ear is only a breath away.\r\nThe intimacy alone will set her heart on fire."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure I get it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Stop that!\r\nGet your mouth away from my ear!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "My perfect kabedon has driven girls crazy for years.\r\nThat's how I became the Kabedon Prince."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "I can't believe people are really into that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "It can be quite a thrill.\r\nMaybe you should take it for a spin, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "A refined guy like you mastering the kabedon?\r\nMan, you'd have girls drooling all over you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Me? Uh, I don't know about this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "It'll be second nature once you get some practice.\r\nYou'll just need to dive into it headfirst."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "How about... Ah, Kamaishi-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Oho? You rang?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "This is Kamaishi-san. She's one of my\r\nmore frequent drinking buddies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "And this here is Kiryu-san, a new pupil in the art\r\nof kabedon. Do you mind if he practices on you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Ohhh, what a fine piece of man!\r\nI'm honored to have been chosen as your first!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "'Kay! Come at me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "The process is simple. Just walk up to Kamaishi-san,\r\nthen place your hand on the wall behind her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "G-Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Okay, here goes nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "I'm ready, Kiryu-san!\r\nCome on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Cool it with the noises!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Next you whisper something sexy\r\nin her ear to ignite the flame in her heart!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Give me all your money."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Oooh, I'll hand over however much you want.\r\nUse it wisely, muscle man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, that was nothing short of a mugging,\r\nand don't give in so easily, Kamaishi-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Why would you think to say something like that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Don't women have a thing for dangerous guys?\r\nI was just trying to spice things up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "That makes sense, but you were giving off a total\r\nshakedown vibe. No girl would ever fall for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Kamaishi... You're not going home tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Ahhh! Hearing that from a big, burly man\r\nlike yourself... I'm so excited!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Well? How was that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Nice work there! You pinned her down with\r\nthe kabedon, then finished her off with a line!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Where are you taking me tonight?\r\nAnywhere you want, hot stuff!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Slow down there.\r\nI was just practicing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Well, ain't that a bummer.\r\nI'm ready whenever you want me, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "U-Uh huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Tonight... You're mine, Kamaishi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Ohhh, I can't wait! A night with this hottie?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "I'm getting all tingly just thinking about it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "You're taking this way too far!\r\nCalm down!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "You're... not bad. It's been ages\r\nsince someone got me this hot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "...Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Not bad, Kiryu-san. For your first kabedon,\r\nthat was actually pretty impressive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "It's tougher than it looks.\r\nI'm surprised you make it seem so simple."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I'm glad you found your calling.\r\nYou're practically a kabedon master."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "Well, maybe so. That said,\r\nit's not always a positive part of my life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "Sometimes I get made fun of on the street\r\nor have to deal with people stalking me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "It's almost impossible to find private time.\r\nThat's why I come here. It's my safe haven."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "By the way, I had a great time today!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Oh, shoot! I've got to be getting to work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "I really appreciate all the help, Kiryu-san.\r\nLet me at least cover your tab. Well, until next time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Right. Good luck with your work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Thanks!\r\nNow then, I'm off!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Hey, we got our asses beat real bad 'cause of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "I've got some pros helping me now, though.\r\nWe're gonna make sure you never kabedon again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Hey, how 'bout giving me one last kabedon first?\r\nSound good?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "I refuse. None of you are worthy\r\nof my prized kabedon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "The fuck you say!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "If it's a kabedon you want so bad,\r\nI'm happy to oblige."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Wait! You're the guy from before...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Stay back, Takayama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "I'm gettin' real sick of you, buddy...\r\nYou're going down this time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Shit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Now where were we...?\r\nStill hoping for that kabedon?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "N-No, I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "You don't have a choice. You're going to\r\ntaste the full force of Takayama's kabedon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "P-Please don't!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Resisting is going to get you hurt.\r\nLet's do this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "Give me all your money...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "A-All right!\r\nJust please don't kill me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "H-Hey, wait up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "You're not going home tonight...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "Please forgive me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "You're mine, punk...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "I-I-I'll give you every last yen I've got!\r\nPlease just let me live!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "You okay, Takayama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah...\r\nRescued by you yet again, Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "And? How was my kabedon?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "It was incredible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Compared to yours, mine is nothing.\r\nKiryu-san, your kabedon even works on guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "If I'm the Kabedon Prince...\r\nyou very well may be the Kabedon King."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "The Kabedon King..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "Well, I really should be going now.\r\nThank you for everything!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "The Kabedon King... Heh.\r\nIt's got a nice ring to it."
msgstr ""

